      "text": "按下Button的委托",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "按下Button的委托",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "j8H7eb1kAiPAC1fh88a6C",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 440.15831823984286,
      "y": 608.7873888048243,
      "width": 1145.1400146484375,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aN",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 985277577,
      "version": 312,
      "versionNonce": 2026843783,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783061294241,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "委托是一种容器，容器里面放的是函数方法。（容器的概念在后面）\n而函数的形式各不相同，参数，返回值各不相同，所以你做委托之前，先得要定义好这个委托容器存放的函数的类型,即委托类型。\n定义了好了函数类型后，将函数加入到委托容器后，你只要触发委托调用\n委托就会帮你把容器里面的每个函数都调用一次,触发的时候和调用普通函数没有区别。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "委托是一种容器，容器里面放的是函数方法。（容器的概念在后面）\n而函数的形式各不相同，参数，返回值各不相同，所以你做委托之前，先得要定义好这个委托容器存放的函数的类型,即委托类型。\n定义了好了函数类型后，将函数加入到委托容器后，你只要触发委托调用\n委托就会帮你把容器里面的每个函数都调用一次,触发的时候和调用普通函数没有区别。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "sZs2MYIx0ZoQUaV6X0G7z",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 440.9398854442119,
      "y": 765.5958600362667,
      "width": 638.0619506835938,
      "height": 548.493288566217,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2014664551,
      "version": 620,
      "versionNonce": 2021212937,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783061304090,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "public delegate void PetName(string name); //委托 (需要一个string类型的参数当宠物名称)\npublic class TestA : MonoBehaviour\n{\n    PetName petName; //声明委托\n \n    void Start()\n    {\n        //委托使用+=来进行\n        petName += Dog; //狗\n        petName += Cat; //猫\n \n        //调用委托事件\n        petName(\"大白\");\n \n    }\n \n    //狗 因为委托调用所以需要一个string参数\n    void Dog(string name)\n    {\n        Debug.Log($\"我叫{name}，是一只狗\");\n    }\n \n    //猫\n    void Cat(string name)\n    {\n        Debug.Log($\"我叫{name}，是一只猫\");\n    }\n}\n",
      "fontSize": 15.13084933975771,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "public delegate void PetName(string name); //委托 (需要一个string类型的参数当宠物名称)\npublic class TestA : MonoBehaviour\n{\n    PetName petName; //声明委托\n \n    void Start()\n    {\n        //委托使用+=来进行\n        petName += Dog; //狗\n        petName += Cat; //猫\n \n        //调用委托事件\n        petName(\"大白\");\n \n    }\n \n    //狗 因为委托调用所以需要一个string参数\n    void Dog(string name)\n    {\n        Debug.Log($\"我叫{name}，是一只狗\");\n    }\n \n    //猫\n    void Cat(string name)\n    {\n        Debug.Log($\"我叫{name}，是一只猫\");\n    }\n}\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
