    },
    {
      "id": "M2zCaUBAwzO_5rTjpH_lg",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 464.57357777072673,
      "y": 1423.4467726877917,
      "width": 1020,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aT",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 758117063,
      "version": 224,
      "versionNonce": 28693097,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783061547434,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "事件在类中声明且生成，且通过使用同一个类或其他类中的委托与事件处理程序关联。包含事件的类用于发布事件。\n这被称为 发布器（publisher） 类。其他接受该事件的类被称为 订阅器（subscriber） 类。\n事件使用 发布-订阅（publisher-subscriber） 模型。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "事件在类中声明且生成，且通过使用同一个类或其他类中的委托与事件处理程序关联。包含事件的类用于发布事件。\n这被称为 发布器（publisher） 类。其他接受该事件的类被称为 订阅器（subscriber） 类。\n事件使用 发布-订阅（publisher-subscriber） 模型。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "v8sZ-mdCm2um14jm-4arc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 459.46322024813526,
      "y": 1538.1294459934466,
      "width": 513.0596923828125,
      "height": 750,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aU",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1733455433,
      "version": 86,
      "versionNonce": 869192839,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783067079416,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": " public static class GameStartEvent\n    {\n        private static Action mOnEventTrigger;\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 注册事件\n        /// </summary>\n        public static void Register(Action onEvent)\n        {\n            mOnEventTrigger += onEvent;\n        }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 注销事件\n        /// </summary>\n        /// <param name=\"onEvent\"></param>\n        public static void UnRegister(Action onEvent)\n        {\n            mOnEventTrigger -= onEvent;\n        }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 触发事件\n        /// </summary>\n        public static void Trigger()\n        {\n            mOnEventTrigger?.Invoke();\n        }\n\n    }",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": " public static class GameStartEvent\n    {\n        private static Action mOnEventTrigger;\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 注册事件\n        /// </summary>\n        public static void Register(Action onEvent)\n        {\n            mOnEventTrigger += onEvent;\n        }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 注销事件\n        /// </summary>\n        /// <param name=\"onEvent\"></param>\n        public static void UnRegister(Action onEvent)\n        {\n            mOnEventTrigger -= onEvent;\n        }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 触发事件\n        /// </summary>\n        public static void Trigger()\n        {\n            mOnEventTrigger?.Invoke();\n        }\n\n    }",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
