    {
      "id": "b4dTRB8Zr5F8tOaPi7FJZ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 486.58382924679574,
      "y": 2406.3714994156703,
      "width": 568.3568041992182,
      "height": 214.9999999999999,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aa",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1634607463,
      "version": 74,
      "versionNonce": 296425767,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783067230831,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "•子节点通知父节点用委托或事件\n•父节点调用子节点可以直接方法调用\n•跨模块通信用事件\n•耦合就是双向引用或循环引用\n•对象之间的交互一般有三种",
      "fontSize": 34.39999999999998,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•子节点通知父节点用委托或事件\n•父节点调用子节点可以直接方法调用\n•跨模块通信用事件\n•耦合就是双向引用或循环引用\n•对象之间的交互一般有三种",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
