      "updated": 1783071111421,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "7.总结",
      "fontSize": 41.33333333333357,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "7.总结",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ht2oA8vdnQCeZJ_7PinYa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2060.444940357903,
      "y": 5276.86753116171,
      "width": 945.983154296875,
      "height": 230.00000000000006,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0p",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1640769543,
      "version": 83,
      "versionNonce": 340206537,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783071205135,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "•表现层 到 底层系统层 用 Command\n•底层系统 到 表现层 用委托或者事件（通知）考虑bindableProperty\n•表现层是可替换的\n•事件由系统层 向 表现层 发送\n•表现层只能用 Command 改变底层系统层的状态（数据）\n•表现层可以直接查询数据",
      "fontSize": 30.66666666666667,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•表现层 到 底层系统层 用 Command\n•底层系统 到 表现层 用委托或者事件（通知）考虑bindableProperty\n•表现层是可替换的\n•事件由系统层 向 表现层 发送\n•表现层只能用 Command 改变底层系统层的状态（数据）\n•表现层可以直接查询数据",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
