      "originalText": "从两个角度去分析模块化",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "n5eSgWgJlukTpn_Fa3YG9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5529.897321310283,
      "y": 332.74848354266123,
      "width": 365.14285714285717,
      "height": 101.4285714285714,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0t",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1267057737,
      "version": 103,
      "versionNonce": 805201481,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783071675840,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "模块对象如何获取？\n如何增加一个模块？",
      "fontSize": 40.57142857142856,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "模块对象如何获取？\n如何增加一个模块？",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "xbDUnN6CoF947acKWIclm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5409.016368929331,
      "y": 505.0580073521851,
      "width": 412.88224456787117,
      "height": 59.5,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0u",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1587036199,
      "version": 108,
      "versionNonce": 562523977,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783071720254,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1.静态类（static）",
      "fontSize": 47.6,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1.静态类（static）",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "LBAJXu-FEYYotSxtfU9ei",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5501.849702262665,
      "y": 593.3913406855186,
      "width": 422.3854724121093,
      "height": 38.99999999999999,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0v",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 737667049,
      "version": 92,
      "versionNonce": 431408393,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783071750010,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CounterModel便是一个静态类",
      "fontSize": 31.199999999999996,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CounterModel便是一个静态类",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "5Rj3SytDFdd82ViDTGXer",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5505.849702262665,
      "y": 647.3913406855186,
      "width": 633.2039428710933,
      "height": 116.99999999999997,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0w",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1033516391,
      "version": 46,
      "versionNonce": 609265287,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783071765748,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "从模块化的两个角度分析如下：\n•静态类可以直接获取\n•扩展一个静态类就是加上一个 static 关键字",
      "fontSize": 31.199999999999992,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "从模块化的两个角度分析如下：\n•静态类可以直接获取\n•扩展一个静态类就是加上一个 static 关键字",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "LXS31gDF8kgdv6nGSrUmN",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5505.849702262665,
      "y": 824.8913406855186,
      "width": 499.19999999999993,
      "height": 38.99999999999999,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0x",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 414466023,
      "version": 178,
      "versionNonce": 834155689,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783071828929,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "静态类虽然十分方便但是问题也存在",
      "fontSize": 31.19999999999999,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "静态类虽然十分方便但是问题也存在",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "-minWq-z-HNwB88KXc-1c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5508.849702262665,
      "y": 872.8913406855186,
      "width": 642.0959033203128,
      "height": 72.00000000000003,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0y",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 994960265,
      "version": 60,
      "versionNonce": 1987287783,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783071830609,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "•静态类没有访问限制。\n•使用 static 去扩展模块，其模块的识别度不高。",
      "fontSize": 28.800000000000008,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•静态类没有访问限制。\n•使用 static 去扩展模块，其模块的识别度不高。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "RM6BmagxIFf31hceEh4Hj",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5429.349702262665,
      "y": 1005.3913406855186,
      "width": 445.63197544642856,
      "height": 60.00000000000001,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0z",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 563535497,
      "version": 73,
      "versionNonce": 104580231,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783071869825,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2.单例（Instance）",
      "fontSize": 48.00000000000001,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2.单例（Instance）",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "-qXfEv6gjKy81Om2XY8ep",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5461.849702262665,
      "y": 1154.5580073521853,
      "width": 1100.287890625,
      "height": 40.00000000000001,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b10",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 553277449,
      "version": 63,
      "versionNonce": 1147833575,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783071915262,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "如果一个模块类是单例类，那么他的访问必须需要通过 模块类.Instance 获取",
      "fontSize": 32,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "如果一个模块类是单例类，那么他的访问必须需要通过 模块类.Instance 获取",
